.TH "MAP.GETORINSERTCOMPUTED" "3JS" "January 22, 2026" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
Map.getOrInsertComputed \- Map.prototype.getOrInsertComputed()
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]getOrInsertComputed()\f[B]\f[R] method of \f[CR]Map\f[R]
instances returns the value corresponding to the specified key in this
\f[CR]Map\f[R].
If the key is not present, it inserts a new entry with the key and a
default value computed from a given callback, and returns the inserted
value.
.PP
Use this method instead of \f[CR]Map.prototype.getOrInsert()\f[R] when
the default value is expensive to compute, and you want to avoid
computing it unless it\(cqs actually needed.
.IP
.EX
\f[B]const\f[R] map = \f[B]new\f[R] Map([[\(dqbar\(dq, \(dqfoo\(dq]]);
\f[B]const\f[R] defaultCreator = (key) \f[B]=>\f[R] \(gadefault for ${key}\(ga;

console.log(map.getOrInsertComputed(\(dqbar\(dq, defaultCreator));
\f[I]// Expected output: \(dqfoo\(dq\f[R]

console.log(map.getOrInsertComputed(\(dqbaz\(dq, defaultCreator));
\f[I]// Expected output: \(dqdefault for baz\(dq\f[R]
.EE
.SH SYNTAX
.IP
.EX
getOrInsertComputed(key, callback)
.EE
.SS Parameters
.TP
\f[B]key\f[R]
The key of the element to return from the \f[CR]Map\f[R] object.
Object keys are compared by reference, not by value.
.TP
\f[B]callback\f[R]
A function that returns the value to insert and return if the key is not
already present in the \f[CR]Map\f[R] object.
The function is called with the following argument:
.RS
.TP
\f[B]key\f[R]
The same key that was passed to \f[CR]getOrInsertComputed()\f[R].
.RE
.SS Return value
The value associated with the specified key in the \f[CR]Map\f[R]
object.
If the key can\(cqt be found, the result of \f[CR]callback(key)\f[R] is
inserted and returned.
.SS Exceptions
.TP
\f[B]TypeError\f[R]
Thrown if \f[CR]callback\f[R] isn\(cqt callable.
.SH EXAMPLES
.SS Avoiding unnecessary default computation
When using \f[CR]Map.prototype.getOrInsert()\f[R], the default value is
computed every time, even if it is not needed.
With \f[CR]getOrInsertComputed()\f[R], the default value is only
computed when necessary.
.IP
.EX
\f[B]const\f[R] map = \f[B]new\f[R] Map([[\(dqbar\(dq, \(dqfoo\(dq]]);
\f[B]const\f[R] defaultCreator = (key) \f[B]=>\f[R] {
  console.log(\(gaCreating default for ${key}\(ga);
  \f[B]return\f[R] \(gadefault for ${key}\(ga;
};

map.getOrInsert(\(dqbar\(dq, defaultCreator(\(dqbar\(dq)); \f[I]// Logs \(dqCreating default for bar\(dq\f[R]
map.getOrInsertComputed(\(dqbar\(dq, defaultCreator); \f[I]// No log\f[R]
.EE
